{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 869746830, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 111, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-28 13:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=869746401,45974302,5997]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62740939]一口糖汽水[/uid] (2026-05-28 13:19):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]在有人在意的角落，白水板块系数要修复昨天的涨幅了[/quote]<br/>我看资金的能力  服不服", "lou": 2820, "content_length": 25, "reply_to": 869746401, "14": {"13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1779945746}, {"pid": 869748821, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 485, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-28 13:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "没事  今天涨了 大家都对 都是开心的 <br/>这种不是我一个人的事<br/>是大家的事 因为大家都站在对的地方<br/><br/>我很感慨 晚上如果有空 咱们说点心里话